name: Complete Photography Contract Bundle
description:
Every form we sell, in one "get your business up and running" bundle!

It's all right here in one bundle. Cute Contracts brings you the official documents you need to run your photography business. Each file includes a logo placeholder and background placeholder. Download will contain a background stripe file that you can change in photoshop and drag right into place! Have control over the stripe color or leave plain.

Custom! Each document can be customized with YOUR logo, and YOUR company information from the Wedding Contract to the Credit Card Authorization Form. Everything is all ready to be customized by you, quickly and easily!

This document bundle includes:

A lawyer-approved Wedding & Portrait Contract* 
Model Release 
DVD/CD Warning Insert 
Comprehensive 5-page shot list for client check-off 
Credit Card Authorization Form. 
Wedding Day Timeline 
Blog Questionare Form 
Three Brand New Items Included! 
Album Order Form 
Location Information 
Cancellation Form 
Cute Contracts makes it so easy. Choose your style: Stripes or plain! 

Where do I print my documents? 
On your home printer on 8.5 x 11 paper. Or you can have them printed at ProDPI, WHCC, or other labs, depending on the paper you want to use. 

What exactly is included?: 

Laywer-Approved Contract - 
bride & groom information 
wedding date and location section 
breakdown of services and products 
payment information 
exclusive photographer 
meal request 
limitation of liability 
and much more!

DVD/CD Warning Insert - How many times have you gotten an email 30 days, 3 months, 1 year after delivering your client's DVD/CD that it won't work, they lost it, etc. etc. Don't waste money making new DVD/CD's for your clients, and protect yourself! Our DVD/CD warning insert includes verbiage notifying clients what actions they must take as soon as they get your DVD/CD. It also notifies them of a charge if they need new copies in the future. This is a must have for anyone who delivers DVD/CD files to their clients! 

Must Have Shot List - This 5 page shot list includes every shot that most couples would want taken. Send it over to them, and have them check off the items they want! 

Timeline Sheet - An hour by hour run through of the wedding day event 

Blog Write Up Form - Simple questions to ask your clients so you can write awesome blog posts about them when you publish their photos! 

Credit Card Authorization Form - Always have your client's credit card information and signature at hand. 

Location Services - Keep track of each location you need to be for the engagement session and wedding! Know exactly where your bride will be getting ready and each stop along the way to the reception. Never get stuck without an address or special location your client's wanted as a photo stop! Includes an area for scouting notes in case you come across something that might be an issue or a great time of day for light at a certain spot. 

Album Order Form - Never forget what album and album choices your client chose! The album order form makes it easy for client's to select their choices! Easily edit the order form to include album companies and cover choices you provide. 

Cancellation Agreement - Should you ever end up in the unfortunate situation of a cancellation, make sure you have the proper form to send to your client's so that you are protected and will not be held liable for their event.

IMPORTANT PRODUCT INFORMATION:

State laws vary dramatically, so you must make sure your custom contract applies to your states laws. Our contract does cover almost everything you will need to be protected, but make sure to consult a lawyer prior to use to ensure you are legally covered for your area, and your specific business needs.

File will be delivered via email receipt after purchase! Just click the link in the email confirmation.

name: Welcome Baby Facebook or Email Expressions
description:
Ever take newborn photos and wish you could get your company name in front of all your client's friends and family? 

Add these adorable facebook expressions to your client's facebook page, or send them via email to welcome their baby! Keep your name in front of your client and all of their friend's by congratulating them via facebook. Upload the expression on their personal page, tag your company and it will show up on your business page and their personal page! You can also send these via email as a nice little congratulations note. 

You can also upload these right onto your business page and tag your client's or use the designs for cards, marketing etc. The possibilities are endless!

We will integrate it with the contract design and send you the printed contracts via snail mail :).
